l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">络</span>我們<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300c1d7de2c0c113f90eaa7531933af879a7be77","tid":266704,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁施sir會唔會好似柒警咁仲有糧出<br />\n<br />\n幫補下都好</blockquote><br />\n肯撚定係警隊條例嘅最低標準"},{"pid":"2c2470c68890d2f36dbfcf1c1147d463d21e6a5f","tid":266704,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港咁樣都唔會有人覺得好嬲<br />\n無人覺得要做啲嘢<br />\n最重要係要返工</blockquote><br />\n唔番工邊個養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b92f83962c1a79fec19675b17f1e8972dd4adc","tid":266704,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:38:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161026/00176_032.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161026%2F00176_032.html&d=36gJMVNU5t%2Ft%2FhIlfzRpcV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=da2aa15d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161026/00176_032.html</a><br />\n<br />\n在fb群組貼兩同袍資料<br />\n已被停職的被告施恒，承認於前年十一月廿七日，在北角警署取用屬警務處的電腦，目的是為自己不誠實地獲益。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，警方於前年十一月廿八日作網上巡邏，在facebook「反佔中認人組」群組中，發現用戶「Tonic Shepherd」在前一天貼上警察內聯網電話簿資料截圖，分屬於兩警員，並留言「有在場人士透露在場警員不斷挑釁市民，警員編號如下：PC&times;&times;&times;、PC&times;&times;&times;&times;&times; 如發現有其他警員挑釁或使用武力，請記低編號及影相，感謝」。<br />\n<br />\n唔係告爆七警料喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd9cbfe93cdc53429d1e62a123a38f50ad2350d","tid":266704,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:40:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161026/19812520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161026%2F19812520&d=36gJMVNU5t%2Ft%2FhIlfzRpcV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2c5dc15e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161026%2F19812520&h=3856411c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161026/19812520</a><br />\n<br />\n案情指警方前年11月28日作網上巡邏，發現前一天在名為「反佔中認人組」的facebook群組裏，用戶「Tonic Shepherd」因應網民的起底要求，上載了兩名警員的警察內聯網電話簿資料的截圖，並留言：「有在場人士透露在場警員不斷挑釁市民，警員編號如下：PC8719、PC13109，如發現有其他警員挑釁或使用武力，請記低編號及影相，感謝。」<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個 PC 背景係咪硬到可以郁到 IP 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d37a57358280a4cb7ad4880f85c5623d4efc100","tid":266704,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T00:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55823288&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55823288%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161025&d=36gJMVNU5t%2Ft%2FhIlfzRpcV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3bf600dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55823288%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161025&h=c996bab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55823288&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161025</a><br />\n<br />\n被指在前年佔領運期間於警隊內任「無間道」助網民起警員底的督察，在調查期間被指其電腦內藏有逾270項兒童色情影像及照片，督察被控不誠實取用電腦及管有兒童色情物品罪，他今在區院承認不誠實取用電腦罪，但否認管有兒童色情物品罪，案件將於明天開審。<br />\n<br />\n認咗不誠實使用電腦都仲要審八日?"},{"pid":"4a90bbf70ee281e9d5d87e4a6d2b3babd9b0322a","tid":266704,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim